<xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" n="sb;3;6733" targOrder="U" to="DITTO" type="reprint from">SB3,6733;PEdg27</xref></head><div lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="edition"><div n="r" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Ἀπολλώνιος Ζήνωνι χαίρειν. ὁ βασιλεὺς συνέτασσεν ἡμῖν 

    <lb n="2"/>δισπορῆσαι τὴν γῆν. ὡς ἂν οὖν ἐχθερίσηις τὸν πρώιον σῖτον, 

    <lb n="3"/>εὐθέως πότισον τὴν γῆν ἀπὸ <choice><corr>χειρός</corr><sic>χερος</sic></choice>, ἐὰν δὲ μὴ δυνατὸν ἦι, 


    <lb n="4"/>κηλώνεια ἐπιστήσας πλείονα οὕτω πότιζε, μὴ πλείους δὲ 

    <lb n="5"/>πέντε <num value="5"/> ἡμερῶν σύσχηις τὸ ὕδωρ, καὶ καταψύξας εὐθέως 

    <lb n="6"/>κατάσπειρε τὸν τρίμηνον πυρόν. γράψον δὲ καὶ πρὸς ἡμᾶς 

    <lb n="7"/>πότε δύνασαι θερίζειν τὸν σῖτον. 

    <lb n="8"/>ἔρρωσο. <expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> <num value="30">λ</num>, Δίου <num value="13">ιγ</num>, Ἁθὺρ <num value="3">γ</num>. 
</ab></div><div n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="9"/>Ζήνωνι. <gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/>σπόρου. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.803" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.803" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="-256" notBefore="-256" type="textDate" value="-0256-12-27">27. Dez. 256 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.803" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Cair. Zen.</title><biblScope type="volume">2</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">59155</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">803</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="DDbDP"><series>0092</series>; <biblScope type="volume">2</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">59155</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0092;2;59155" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.803" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">IX</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">51</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">X</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">37</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">XI</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">55</biblScope></bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.803" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p><bibl default="NO" type="illustration">Pl. VI</bibl><bibl default="NO" type="illustration">Montevecchi, Papirologia, Tav. 13</bibl><bibl default="NO" type="illustration">Peremans - Vergote, Pap